  <text>
    <body>
      <ab type="lido:objectWorkType">Leaflet</ab>
      <ab subtype="creation" type="lido:event">
        <date>1952 after</date>
      </ab>
      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The leaflet features a frameless collage of a photograph and a graphic illustration. The photograph in the background shows the head of a man with a moustache in a sombrero. His mouth is open. The illustration in the forefront shows a man on a galloping horse trying to lift a woman onto his steed. In the background, a group of men on horses are giving chase. The logo of film production company ‘20th Century Fox’ is printed on the leaflet’s centre right. The original film title is printed above the images.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The film was directed by Elia Kazan and released in 1952.</ab>
